Uses of Package
sg.yeefan.searchenginewrapper

Packages that use sg.yeefan.searchenginewrapper
sg.yeefan.searchenginewrapper Provides a wrapper framework for unifying programatic access to search engines. 
sg.yeefan.searchenginewrapper.clients Provides search engine clients, all of which subclassed from SearchEngineClient or KeyedSearchEngineClient.
